Terms of Service
Effective Date: October 2025

Welcome to Giải Mã Crypto (“we,” “our,” or “us”). These Terms of Service govern your use of our automated content system, including integrations with TikTok, YouTube, or Facebook for publishing educational content about cryptocurrency and technology.

1. Use of Service
Our system allows authorized users to automatically upload and publish approved videos via secure API integration. Users are responsible for ensuring that all uploaded content complies with TikTok’s Community Guidelines and applicable laws.

2. Content Ownership
All uploaded videos remain the property of their respective creators. We do not claim ownership or redistribute your content outside your intended channels.

3. Data Security
We temporarily store access tokens in encrypted form for API publishing purposes only. No permanent data storage occurs on our servers.

4. Limitation of Liability
We are not responsible for penalties or account restrictions due to content policy violations on third-party platforms.

5. Contact
